  ;; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  ;; BRIDGE RECTIFIER — D1 (top-left), D2 (top-right), D3 (bot-left), D4 (bot-right)
  ;; Bridge centre at (65, 60). Diodes oriented to route current:
  ;;   PROBE_A (top) → bridge → HV+
  ;;   PROBE_B (bottom) → bridge → GND
  ;; D1: anode=PROBE_A  cathode=HV+   at (55, 45) angle=0
  ;; D2: anode=GND_node cathode=PROBE_A  at (75, 45) angle=0  (reverse branch)
  ;; D3: anode=PROBE_B  cathode=HV+   at (55, 75) angle=0
  ;; D4: anode=GND_node cathode=PROBE_B  at (75, 75) angle=0
